{"title":"彩霞满天，火光灿烂","authors":["沙鸥"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":1,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩霞满天，火光灿烂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙鸥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎明，用光亮的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉开一九五九年的窗户，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我看见一片灿烂的火光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像迎接太阳的彩霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从西印度群岛和非洲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熊熊地升腾而起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大海掀起玫瑰的波涛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴和刚果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用雪亮的长剑"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺在殖民主义者的心上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那黑透了的心房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流着污秽的血水。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用什么来描绘我的喜悦？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五九年是这样开始！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我伸出双臂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我用歌声和诗句，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进入我兄弟的行列，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一块战斗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这时，在大西洋岸边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加勒比海旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那像翡翠一样的国土上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传来了握紧拳头的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"格吱吱的响声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈瓦那的街道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正被百万人的示威震动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么威风的队伍！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像十二级台风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"卷着愤怒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼啸着，飞旋着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向白宫扫去——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不准干涉内政！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这最甜的国家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流过最酸的眼泪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴君的苦刑与屠杀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只埋下仇恨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴蒂斯塔政权终于败亡了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像铁锤下腐烂的鸡蛋；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的敌人逃到美国的口袋中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而美国，满头大汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还想伸手捏碎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古巴用鲜血夺来的独立。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这只是梦想！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六百万人的臂膀是一道墙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六百万人的心是冲天的烈火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六百万人的脚步是滔滔洪流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"碰不垮！浇不熄！挡不住！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旋风呼应着旋风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火光辉映着火光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越过茫茫的大洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刚果河正在激怒地奔流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金刚石正在划破"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"殖民主义者的脚掌。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那“安定的绿洲”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早就风雨满楼了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八十年的痛苦与屈辱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写了厚厚一本账簿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火山口喷出白热的岩浆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"城市与丛林"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"复仇的枪口瞄准敌人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要砸碎奴役的枷锁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要摧毁殖民统治！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比利时王朝失魂落魄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血腥镇压"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与空头的“独立”支票，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全不管用了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜红的旗帜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民族解放的旗帜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起来了！举起来了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从古巴，从刚果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从拉丁美洲，从非洲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高高地举起来了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在东方的欢笑中举起来了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像遮天盖地的云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像烈焰喧腾的火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"压死帝国主义！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧死帝国主义！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩霞满天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火光灿烂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砍断铁链的声音，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成了宏伟的美妙的音乐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请托着我的歌声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"请照亮我的诗句，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的歌声和诗句，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快飞吧！快飞吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞向海浪抚爱着的古巴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞向神话般的刚果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告诉我正在战斗的兄弟："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在支援"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}